s were not released. . His Columbia Thesis paper was not released.</p>\n<p>His Harvard College records were not released.  His Selective Service Registration was not released.  His medical records were not released.  His Law Practice client list was not released.  A Certified Copy of his original birth certificate was not released. Neither was a signed Certification of\nLive Birth released.</p>\n<p>He had no Harvard Law Review articles published, or University of Chicago\narticles.  Neither was his Illinois State Senate records.</p>\n<p>He was the ultimate Manchurian candidate who literally betrayed our nation\u2019s laws, and opened the door for our demise as a nation.</p>\n<p>A person with 143 days of experience couldn\u2019t get a manager\u2019s job at Wal-Mart.  But, he was installed as President of the most powerful nation on earth.</p>\n<p>Go figure</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 151, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2021373819320139985", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASFhP7pNY", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 36, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8411868, "raw_content": "", "author": "LiberaIPussyGuy", "created": 1770781615305, "profile_picture": "kUZP54YGIYuT", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Ignimbrite_FlareUp20", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASFhP7pNY.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/KathleenWinche3/status/2021373819320139985?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurha